Ga On, I said wake up.

19
00:03:42,890 --> 00:03:47,640
Elijah, what brings you here at this time?

20
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:50,320
- Yo Han is gone. 
 - Huh?

21
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:55,430
You heard me, Yo Han is gone! I woke up but he wasn't there.

22
