348
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:09,710
I will tighten the security and check Jeong Seon Ah's movements.

349
00:36:15,080 --> 00:36:16,910
Chief, earlier—

350
00:36:16,910 --> 00:36:19,460
Lieutenant Yun Su Hyeon, Seoul Metropolitan Investigation Unit team one.

